Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂家果然很了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還招待我們來這種規模的溫泉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了這麼多人  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  非常歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像這溫泉跟父親的公司有些聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是免費入場的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何時候都可以請你們來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威夷和迪拜的溫泉也是免費入場的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這一瞬間我體會到了差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂真是凌駕我們標準之上啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說  還真是讓人瞠目結舌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始強攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起尺寸更重要的是敏感度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏感度？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏感度？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏感度…是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠  虧你能靜得下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  像你這麼坐立不安更奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在桂她們全在旁邊的溫泉裏入浴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人之心在亢奮  你就不想看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能付諸於行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當這是漫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直要發瘋了  就這樣站著…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}好了…好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這水很舒服哦  不進來嗎  這裏是混浴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  混浴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混浴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你們的  真單純
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣算是幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個想法說明我們還是太年輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經到這個時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  世界準備怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼特別要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒謊  那個不給伊藤麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  給誠的是人情巧克力  人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上這麼說  其實是真命巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能  倒是光你準備怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑田終於要跟澤永告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要給的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在考慮「該怎麼辦呢」的階段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.69,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只給巧克力的話太可惜了  這可是個好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  看上澤永  黑田的趣味還真不雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩人也是  真容易看穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  客人們都看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是為情人節做準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不準備給誰巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把年紀了  還情人節？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人不管到了幾歲也是少女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是世界  你有中意的男孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我孩子  心裏想的都寫在臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你  作巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我不擅長做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那沒關係  重要的是心意  心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  還有就是印象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能做出一旦入口就回味無窮的那種味道的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成這樣的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能深深地刺入他的心窩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要刺進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  直搗心窩  需要主動出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不會出擊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊  出擊  出擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふんぐるい　むぐるうなふ\Nくとぅるふ　るるいえ  うが·なぐる　ふたぐん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふんぐるい　むぐるうなふ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（咒語，意為邪神Cthulhu的歸來）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  加納的可可塊不能立即到貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只能用現有的東西做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要  人魚的眼淚和…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個也放進去吧  曼佗羅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節當天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天2月14日的戀愛運是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「意想不到會是她積極主動地來接近你」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  在進教室前沒任何人給你東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還期待著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:08:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  懷著對我愛慕之心的少女是個怕羞的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「並且會同意和你一起跨過成人的那道坎」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠  成人的那道坎是什麼滋味的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去看一下鞋箱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也好好看一下桌子裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}沒有  沒有  完全沒有  連渣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  青春這個混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不太好  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要一個人跨過成人的那道坎嗎  誠這個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  雖說我和伊藤之間事到如今才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這場景不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…難道…難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人情巧克力  人情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今給伊藤這種人也真是失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  你也是人情版的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人情的 人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  人情啊  什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那個是人情巧克力的  沒必要收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠  加藤同學的那個是人情的吧  是人情的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優柔寡斷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個總之先靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是特意通宵做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊  考慮了3天3夜才選好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收下的話不管哪個只能選一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個都是人情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我為了誠君  努力做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的對手出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做巧克力真是很難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說  這個好像不是人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今  今天就收下這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤…  誠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠君…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪個我都得死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  誠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個不注意  又到哪裏去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}喂  那手上是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠  你在說什麼胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和姐姐一～起～吃～嗎～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼世界的媽媽也來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下我吧  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小心都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無處可逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠君  我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐來告訴你成人之禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輩子都可以叫你「哥哥」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  要我只選一個怎麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛快的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下有那種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  把大家的都吃了吧  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會有不少神秘的味道  肯定是好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感想和答覆  請等下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  白色情人節？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真期待下個月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於解放了  到底要怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  是清浦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「什麼嘛」可真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你嚇我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做虧心事  不怕鬼敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可以這麼做  但也不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  拳擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要誤會  是人情巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣  是嗎  是人情的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要的話…也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜  真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你  我精神多了  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  既然有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個才是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  清浦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心意我領了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:15:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是當面給會害羞  我也是受人之托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰  誰的…委託？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤永…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實比小說還突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣算是幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個想法  說明我們還是太年輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的青春  墜向更深的混沌之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:17:04.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}忘れてたこんな気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:10.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}閉じられた扉の奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:18.50,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}鍵をかけ　開け方もわすえてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:23.18,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}わたしのこころ　ほどけてゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:30.89,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}それはあなたの魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:37.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}指が笑顔が声が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:45.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}いつのまにか開けてしまう　素敵だね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:51.21,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}隣には優しい瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:58.06,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}ずっと　さがしてた言葉を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:18:04.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}いつまでも言えずにいた　けれど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:11.32,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}kiss me,baby　キスして　やさしく
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:17.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}ほほに陽だまりの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:24.60,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}淡いぬくもりを残して
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:27.92,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}ずっとずっと二人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:30.85,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:17:04.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}早已忘卻的這份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:10.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}藏在緊閉心門的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:18.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}緊緊鎖住　甚至忘記如何開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:23.18,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}我的心扉　漸漸敞開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:30.89,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}被你的魔法喚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:37.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}你的手指　笑容和聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:45.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}悄悄叩開我的心　美妙絕倫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:51.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}身旁是你溫柔的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:58.06,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}尋覓已久的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:18:04.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}羞於啟齒　卻要鼓起勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:11.32,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\rEDJ\frz-90}kiss{\fscx50}　{\fscx100}me,baby{\rEDC\frz-90}　給我溫柔的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:17.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}臉龐印上朝陽的吻痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:24.60,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}伴著淡淡的溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:27.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}兩人相依而行
